s:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/oppenheimer-trailer-shows-chris-nolans-take-on-the-birth-of-the-atomic-bomb-152022327.html"><em>《奥本海默》</em></a> 。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>有关<em>您如何生活的</em>详细信息？稀疏。吉卜力工作室尚未发布这部电影的预告片，也没有购买任何电视广告。事实上，这是迄今为止它为<em>《How Do You Live?》</em>所做的唯一促销活动。是工作室<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://gizmodo.com/miyazaki-ghibli-how-do-you-live-poster-trailer-anime-1850499515">上个月发布的</a>单张海报。本片为原创作品，但以吉野源三郎 1937 年的同名小说命名。宫崎骏在接受采访时表示，这本书在他的电影主角的生活中发挥了重要作用。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/hayao-miyazakis-final-film-will-be-studio-ghiblis-first-imax-release-195624834.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/hayao-miyazakis-final-film-will-be-studio-ghiblis-first-imax-release-195624834.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ddb14b48-fc93-4b86-ba2d-08b8e101bf78</guid><dc:creator>伊戈尔·博尼法西奇</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jul 2023 19:56:24 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688846189</ingested><modified> 2023-07-08T19:56:37+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[Movies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Igor Bonifacic]]></category><media:content height="2453" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/f7a22f10-1dc8-11ee-a3ff-b679dc6e70a7" width="3500"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[