ubDate><ingested> 1688660914</ingested><modified> 2023-07-06T16:28:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1250" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/e5b63320-1c18-11ee-bd7e-ce792fdc78d0" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1250" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/e5b63320-1c18-11ee-bd7e-ce792fdc78d0" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Cherlynn Low / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[An image of a Google Nest Hub on a bedside table.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Google Nest Hub]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Google Calendar allows users to indicate their location at specific times of the day]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>谷歌<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://techcrunch.com/2023/07/07/google-calendar-now-lets-users-specify-where-theyre-working-from-throughout-the-day/">扩展了</a><a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-calendar-time-insights-meetings-workspace-144136600.html">日历</a>的现有功能，为用户提供了一种简单的方法，让他们的同事知道在一天中的不同时间可以联系到他们。早在 2021 年，该公司就首次推出了“工作地点”，允许用户通过日程安排指示他们的工作地点。但现在，他们可以在日历中设置一天中特定时段的工作地点，以便更准确地反映他们的工作地点。可用性。</p><p>正如谷歌在其<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://workspaceupdates.googleblog.com/2023/07/adding-more-flexibility-to-working-location-google-calendar.html">公告</a>中所说，对于那些拥有混合工作环境的人来说，在不同地点工作是很常见的。此功能可以让同事更轻松地确定他们是否可以进行面对面协作，或者是否必须安排视频会议。要使用该功能，他们可以创建一个事件并选择工作位置，然后选择时间范围并指示他们在这些时间段内的位置。升级后的工作地点功能现已面向所有 Google Workspace 商务标准版、商务 Plus 版、企业标准版、企业 Plus 版、教育基础版、教育标准版、教育 Plus版、教学升级版和公益用户推出。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/29f29f10-1d8b-11ee-adff-9c793a51c73b" style="height:1032px;width:1600px;" alt="谷歌日历的屏幕截图。" data-uuid="c9fa8543-55c2-341f-aa8f-1a9eeec87348"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">谷歌</div></figure><p>这家科技巨头还<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://9to5google.com/2023/07/07/google-docs-edit-mode-android/">让</a>Google Docs 对创作者更加友好。当用户启动应用程序并在 Android 设备上打开文档文件时，它现在将以<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://workspaceupdates.googleblog.com/2023/07/release-notes-07-07-2023.html">编辑模式启动</a>。不再需要点击编辑按钮 - 他们现在可以直接进入文档并立即开始输入或更改内容。点击打开的文档将立即调出屏幕键盘，除非他们的设备连接了物理键盘。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/google-calendar-allows-users-to-indicate-their-location-at-specific-times-of-the-day-130114707.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/google-calendar-allows-users-to-indicate-their-location-at-specific-times-of-the-day-130114707.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> b13094dd-5939-4b86-9b88-5ba9ba49d78b</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jul 2023 13:01:14 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688825996</ingested><modified> 2023-07-08T14:19:59+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><ca